ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectSpecial Economic Measures (Iran) Regulations
PrecisSPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (IRAN) REGULATIONS, to impose additional sanctions above and beyond those imposed by the United Nations Security Council in order to hamper the growth of Iran's nuclear program to the greatest possible extent, and persuade Iran's leadership to resume negotiations with respect to its nuclear program.
